## Second Half Microgames

### Dinosaur Run Microgame
- Use `Space` to jump and avoid the incoming spikes.

### Radio Signal Microgame
- Adjust the `Amplitude` and `Frequency` to make the waves match.

### Simon Says Microgame
- Click on the highlighted squares to replicate the sequence. Do it three times to complete the game.

### Door Microgame
- Interact with the terminals in the room in a specific order to open the door.

### Musical Notes Microgame
- Use `A`, `W`, and `D` to play a game similar to guitar hero and complete the notes. Get enough right to advance.